ZH: 通过安检前，所有乘客必须脱下鞋子。
EN: Before going through security check, all passengers must take off their shoes.

ZH: 在机场安检时，请把手提包放在传送带上检查。
EN: When going through airport security, please put your handbag on the conveyor belt for inspection.

ZH: 孩子们表现很好，很快就通过了安检。
EN: The children behaved well and passed through security quickly.

ZH: 安检人员会用金属探测器检查乘客的物品。
EN: Security personnel will use a metal detector to check passengers' belongings.

ZH: 他们在过安检的时候发现了一把匕首。
EN: They found a knife during the security check.

ZH: 请在安检时把所有液体物品放在透明袋子里。
EN: Please put all liquid items in a transparent bag during security check.

ZH: 各位乘客，请准备好身份证件以便安检。
EN: Passengers, please have your identification ready for security check.

ZH: 做好安检工作是确保航空安全的重要措施。
EN: Conducting security checks is an important measure to ensure aviation safety.

ZH: 安检的目的是防止危险品和违禁品携带上飞机。
EN: The purpose of security check is to prevent dangerous and prohibited items from being brought onto the plane.

ZH: 有些乘客对安检程序不够了解，导致耽误时间。
EN: Some passengers are not familiar with the security check procedures, leading to delays.

ZH: 如果有任何疑问，请向安检人员咨询。
EN: If you have any questions, please consult the security personnel.

ZH: 安检工作需要严格遵守相关规定和标准。
EN: Security check work needs to strictly adhere to relevant regulations and standards.

ZH: 安检设备保证了机场和车站的安全性。
EN: The security screening equipment ensures the safety of airports and train stations.

ZH: 学生们参观了机场的安检中心，了解了安检的流程。
EN: Students visited the airport security center and learned about the security check process.

ZH: 我们必须严格遵守安检规定，不得带有违禁品。
EN: We must strictly comply with security regulations and must not carry prohibited items.

ZH: 在机场安检队列中，请排好队伍，等待您的轮到。
EN: In the airport security line, please line up and wait for your turn.

ZH: 安检处的人员很忙，要用礼貌对待他们。
EN: The personnel at the security checkpoint are busy, so please treat them with courtesy.

ZH: 请把所有金属物品放在托盘里过安检。
EN: Please put all metal items in the tray when going through security check.

ZH: 机场安检在确保安全上起着重要作用。
EN: Airport security checks play an important role in ensuring safety.

ZH: 安检过程通常需要乘客合作并配合以完成。
EN: The security check process usually requires the cooperation and coordination of passengers to complete.
